<latemp_meta_desc "Maintenance version of libtap" />

<p>
libtap is a library to implement <a href="http://testanything.org/">the
Test Anything Protocol</a> for C originally created by Nik Clayton. This is a
maintenance branch by me (= Shlomi Fish).
</p>

